  "prompt": "Which are the top 5 Bollywood songs of 2015?",
  "response": "In 2015, several Bollywood songs gained immense popularity and topped the charts. Here are five of the most notable ones:\n\n1. **\"Gerua\"** - From the movie *Dilwale*, this romantic track featuring Shah Rukh Khan and Kajol was sung by Arijit Singh and Antara Mitra, and composed by Pritam.\n\n2. **\"Sheila Ki Jawani\"** - Although released in 2010, it continued to be popular in 2015 due to its frequent play in parties and events. \n\n3. **\"Bole Chudiyan\"** - This song gained renewed popularity with the *Baazigar* movie celebrations.\n\n4. **\"Janam Janam\"** - Another romantic hit from *Dilwale*, sung by Arijit Singh, it became a favorite for its soulful melody.\n\n5. **\"Sooraj Dooba Hain\"** - From the movie *Roy*, this peppy number was sung by Arijit Singh and composed by Amaal Mallik.\n\nThese songs were widely appreciated and played across various platforms, making them some of the top tracks of 2015.",
